          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". We sadly have another incident, this one killing a second-gen in what we would call a senseless act of nature. A local news report didn’t say what the cause of the fire was and neither did the fire department.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
